q<character>                            Will start recording a macro and store in register <character>
    gg                                  Go to top of file
    O                                   Insert line above top line
    <text>                              Write text on line
    :w                                  Save file
    :bn                                 Go to next file
    :q                                  Stop recording macro
    @<register_char>                    Execute macro
    3@<register_char>                   Or execute macro 3 times